# Intuition
As we must count the number of characters from the leaf node, we use DFS.

# Approach
We just traverse the graph using DFS. Whenever we visit the node mark it as visited and if its children are not visited, visit them.

Here First let us previous count of the label because the count is from parent and after traversal we get total count of label. Now total count of label - previous count of label is current count of label.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(N+M)

- Space complexity:
O(H) where is maximum height of the tree.

