So the basic idea of the code is to, call all children of the node and they will return frequency array(which will have constant size of 26) telling frequency of all different labels, which we will add to current frequency array. Then we will also add current node label in frequency array. 
This node answer will be freqArr[currentLabel].
And then we will return this array.
