# Approach
With the help of DFS, we **go down to the leaves of the tree**, **calculate the frequency of each label** for them (there is only one label for leaves). After raising to a higher level, we **add to the frequency of labels of the current node the frequency of labels of all child nodes**.

**Don't forget to update the result**.

